# Segment pills (Mandatory)

Full contract: [Segment-Pill-Standard.md](../../docs/02_FLUTTER_MIGRATION/Segment-Pill-Standard.md)

## Decision tree

| Role | Widget | Tier |
| --- | --- | --- |
| 2–4 equal page tabs | `VitTabBar.segment` / `VitSegmentedTabBar` | S1 (~28px) |
| MUA/BÁN, Long/Short | `VitSegmentedChoice` / `.buySell()` | S2 (44px) |
| Preset % row | `VitPresetChipRow` | S3 (34px) |
| Filter / category chips | `VitFilterChip` / `VitChoicePill` | S4 (44px) |

## Banned in features (P0)

Do not add: `class _FilterButton`, `_FilterTabs`, `_NetworkFilterTabs`, `_AuditFilterTabs`, `_SegmentedTabs`.

## Banned in features (P1)

Do not add: `class _FilterChip`, `_ChipButton`, `_ChoiceChipButton`, `_FilterChips`, `_DomainFilterChip`, `_FilterChipButton`, `_TimeFilterChips`, `_CategoryFilterChips`, `_StatusFilterChips`.

## Verify before batch complete

```bash
cd flutter_app
dart run tool/segment_pill_audit.dart --check --strict-full
dart run tool/segment_pill_manifest.dart --check
flutter test test/quality/segment_pill_guardrail_test.dart --reporter=compact
```
